formTag.name: We, Manch Technologies Private Limited (Manch) and United Breweries Limited (UBL) respect your privacy and in your interest informs you that we may process data about you that can identify you and be termed as your personal data.
We may process your personal data in accordance with the details mentioned hereinbelow:
1. Name and phone number of the licensee
4. GST certificate details of the establishment

We may collect, process, store, use, transfer, and maintain your personal data in line with the relevant applicable data retention guidelines/rules for the purpose of performing a KYC check/any other verification
based on which UBL may determine whether to initiate or maintain a business relationship with you/your organization.

You hereby consent to the collection, processing, storage, use, transfer, and maintenance of your personal data for the purpose stated above from yourself, authorized consumer reporting agencies, government sources, other authorized personnel
and entities having information about you for verification purpose. Your personal data will be handled in accordance with applicable data protection laws and regulations.
You hereby provide that all the information furnished hereunder for screening purpose should be true to best of your knowledge.
Any copy, whether electronic or otherwise, of the documents provided for verification shall be equally legally valid as the original.
In case you wish to exercise your rights as a data principal or withdraw your consent for processing, please contact us at privacyoffice@ubmail.com.
